set(auto).
assign(max_seconds, 5).
assign(max_mem, 1024).
# Predicates:
Suck(x) ::: x sucks.
Vacuum(x) ::: x is a vacuum.
Vampire(x) ::: x is a vampire.
Space(x) ::: x is space.
Duster(x) ::: x is a duster.
HouseholdAppliance(x) ::: x is a household appliance.

# Premises:
Suck(plungers)
Suck(vacuums)
Suck(vampires)
∀x (Space(x) → Vacuum(x))
∀x (Duster(x) → HouseholdAppliance(x))
∀x (HouseholdAppliance(x) ∧ Duster(x) → ¬Suck(x))

# Conclusion:
∀x (IsHouseholdAppliance(x) → Suck(x))
